{"tid":561730,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"係咩理由支撐你繼續行落去？","createTime":"2018-02-15T08:53:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T11:38:38.000Z","uid":64065,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f06d95033bc12648496877f9e69843de443e4680","tid":561730,"uid":64065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T08:53:59.000Z","msg":"同男朋友一齊就快一年，到而家都仲成日鬧交。我地兩個嘅性格都好強硬，所以成日鬧交不歡而散，期間互相唔搵對方，然後拖到有一方讓步先會冇事。其實導致鬧交嘅原因唔係啲咩大事，反而係大家期間個處理方法同埋態度先係最傷害大家。我想講其實放棄真係好容易，選擇留低繼續先最需要勇氣，你明唔明？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edafdf9a74f59d2f21362281a2cd328c31c147dc","tid":561730,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T09:22:34.000Z","msg":"噉點解你兩個唔一齊攞出嚟討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a81853c5e27328af9b7757e43dfc78b1b65462b","tid":561730,"uid":91884,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T10:48:52.000Z","msg":"面子緊要過段關係"},{"pid":"d1de699bd739c243e13abe749a51815385fd29d3","tid":561730,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T11:08:07.000Z","msg":"Can&rsquo;t pretend anymore"},{"pid":"6b4311607711ad69a4d192df5f0de78d49ed9df9","tid":561730,"uid":39065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a81853c5e27328af9b7757e43dfc78b1b65462b","tid":561730,"uid":91884,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T10:48:52.000Z","msg":"面子緊要過段關係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T11:38:38.000Z","msg":"即係仲係愛自己多過愛對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}